==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Three-mile
<hw>Three"-mile`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to three
miles; <as>as, <col><b>the three-mile limit</b></col>, or the limit of
the marine belt (the <mcol><col><b>three-mile belt</b></col> <it>or</it>
<col><b>three-mile zone</b></col></mcol>) of three miles included in
territorial waters (which see) of a state</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Three-nerved</ent>⟦br⟧
